	course\, students will learn the ins-and-outs of Serato\, playing and mixi
	ng tracks\, finessing your tracks\, and general tips and tricks for digita
	l DJ-ing.\n\n*Use of a laptop is required to take part in this class — Ver
	a has a limited number of laptops available to borrow for membership. If y
	ou need one to participate\, please email yewon.k@theveraproject.org to co
